[Brisbane is the capital and most populous city in the Australian state of Queensland and the 3rd most populous city in Australia. Brisbane's metropolitan area has a population of 2.2 million. It can be located in the map of Queensland at: http://au.totaltravel.yahoo.com/destinations/maps/australia/qld/.

Vulnerability to outbreaks of measles virus infection is a consequence of incomplete vaccine coverage and an abundance of non-resident tourists. - Mod.CP

